#, no-wrap
msgid "This chapter describes how to install and configure the X Window System providing a graphical environment"
msgstr ""
"Este capítulo describe cómo instalar y configurar el Sistema X Window para "
"proporcionar un entorno gráfico"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: part
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Part I. Getting Started"
msgstr "Parte I. Primeros pasos"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Chapter 5. The X Window System"
msgstr "Capítulo 5. El Sistema X Window"

#. type: Title =
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "The X Window System"
msgstr "El Sistema X Window"

#. type: Title ==
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "Sinopsis"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:61
msgid ""
"An crossref:bsdinstall[bsdinstall-synopsis,installation] of FreeBSD using "
"man:bsdinstall[8] does not automatically install a graphical user "
"interface.  This chapter describes how to install and configure the man:"
"Xorg[1] server, which provides the open source X Window System (colloquially "
"X11) used to provide a graphical environment."
msgstr ""
"Una crossref:bsdinstall[bsdinstall-synopsis,installation] de FreeBSD "
"utilizando man:bsdinstall[8] no instala automáticamente una interfaz gráfica "
"de usuario. Este capítulo describe cómo instalar y configurar el servidor "
"man:Xorg[1], el cual proporciona el sistema de código abierto X Window ("
"coloquialmente X11) utilizado para ofrecer un entorno gráfico."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:63
msgid "Before reading this chapter:"
msgstr "Antes de leer este capítulo:"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:66
msgid ""
"Know how to install additional third-party software as described in crossref:"
"ports[ports,Installing Applications: Packages and Ports]."
msgstr ""
"Sepa cómo instalar software adicional de terceros como se describe en "
"crossref:ports[ports,Instalación de aplicaciones: paquetes y ports]."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:68
msgid "Read this chapter to learn:"
msgstr "Lea este capítulo para aprender cómo:"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:70
msgid "How to select and install drivers for the graphics processor (GPU)."
msgstr "Seleccionar e instalar controladores para el procesador gráfico (GPU)."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:72
msgid ""
"The various components of the X Window System, and how they interoperate."
msgstr ""
"Identificar los diversos componentes del Sistema X Window y su "
"interoperabilidad."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:73
msgid "How to install and configure the X.org server."
msgstr "Instalar y configurar el servidor X.org."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/x11/_index.adoc:74
